 een factuur.</p><ul><li>Voor <strong>2023 </strong>bedraagt de jaarlijkse retributie <strong>136 </strong>euro. </li></ul><p>De bedragen worden jaarlijks geïndexeerd.</p>"},"naam":{"nl":"Kost","nl-BE-x-formal":"Kost","en":"Cost","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Kost"},"@type":"Kost","order":0}],"creatie":"2023-05-04T14:10:36.693493569Z","laatstGewijzigd":"2023-11-14T15:05:47.088607249Z","laatstOntvangen":"2023-11-14T15:05:47.088608128Z","productnummer":"1953","gearchiveerd":false,"publicatieLink":{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","en":"See also on vlaanderen.be"},"url":"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/Product/059dbe0a-7427-41dc-a01b-80a38990e67c"},"metadata":{"uJeVersie":"32.3.0","generatedFormeleFields":true,"generatedInformeleFields":true},"@id":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantiesnapshot/4a8a386d-1ce1-4942-af08-bdd4d99c9ffc","@type":"InstantieSnapshot","isVersionOf":"https://ipdc.tni-vlaanderen.be/id/instantie/5aa0ca13-498e-45ee-89db-e156e272ad4e"},{"id":"6ae5e923-49c6-465a-87cd-cab5022e15bd","generatedAtTime":"2023-11-14T15:05:45.820114Z","bevoegdBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"uitvoerendBestuursniveaus":["Vlaams"],"naam":{"en":"Recognition as environmental expert in soil corrosion","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Erkenning als milieudeskundige bodemcorrosie ","nl-BE-x-formal":"Erkenning als milieudeskundige bodemcorrosie ","nl":"Erkenning als milieudeskundige bodemcorrosie "},"beschrijving":{"en":"<p>You require Flemish recognition as ‘environmental expert in soil corrosion’ if you investigate whether a cathodic protection must be applied in order to prevent corrosion of an underground container for the storage of hazardous substances or gasses.</p><p><a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.milieudeskundigen_bodemcorrosie.pdf\">List of recognised environmental expert in soil corrosion</a>.</